Objective
Store anonymized patient admissions, discharges, and OT scheduling data.
________________________________________
Create Tables Script
File: sql/create_tables.sql
CREATE TABLE hospital_admissions (
    admission_id INT IDENTITY(1,1),
    patient_id INT,
    department VARCHAR(100),
    ward_name VARCHAR(100),
    bed_type VARCHAR(50),
    admission_date DATETIME,
    discharge_date DATETIME,
    ot_scheduled BIT,
    ot_duration_hours FLOAT,
    status VARCHAR(50)
);
________________________________________
Sample Data Columns
Column	Description
patient_id	Unique patient identifier
department	ICU / Cardiology / Neurology
ward_name	Assigned ward
bed_type	ICU / General / Emergency
admission_date	Admission timestamp
discharge_date	Discharge timestamp
ot_scheduled	OT required or not
ot_duration_hours	Surgery duration
status	Active / Discharged
